WEBVTT

00:00.629 --> 00:03.770
Previously, on AMC's Breaking Bad...

00:10.366 --> 00:13.870
My signatures are all over those boxes.

00:13.990 --> 00:15.703
I cannot be audited.

00:15.823 --> 00:18.080
Circumstances
with the cartel are untenable.

00:18.200 --> 00:19.621
And I need your help.

00:19.741 --> 00:21.828
No one needs to go to Mexico.

00:21.851 --> 00:23.999
The cartel wants your formula.

00:26.879 --> 00:29.663
Now get the fuck out of here
and never come back.

00:30.920 --> 00:41.031
