that I have of my father.

28:34.114 --> 28:38.183
I don't want you to think of
me the way I was last night.

28:41.120 --> 28:42.821
I don't want that

28:42.855 --> 28:44.789
to be the memory you have of me

28:44.823 --> 28:46.324
when I'm gone.

28:48.127 --> 28:51.029
